caption.title: Identification of rotavirus A VP7 gene segment by using Beg9 and End 9 primers.
caption.p: Lane 1: positive control, Lane 2: DNA ladder 50 bp, lane 3, 4, 5, 6, 8, 9, 10, 11, 13: Amplified product of gene segment VP7(1062 bp size) of samples no 1, 2, 3, 4, 6, 7, 9, 12 and 15, Lane7, 12: Samples number 5, 13 negative for VP7 gene, Lane 14, 15: Negative control and non-target control(NT-C), respectively.
